Package task.graphModel

Class Edge<V,E extends Number>

java.lang.Object
task.graphModel.Edge<V,E>
Type Parameters:
V - the type of data stored in the vertices
E - the type of weight associated with the edge (must extend Number)
public class Edge<V,E extends Number> extends Object
Represents an edge in a graph connecting two vertices with a specified weight.
